Policy and Terms
Introduction
At Easy-to-Use Mobile App Studio, we prioritize the protection of your privacy and the security of your data. Our Policy and Terms outline the rules and guidelines that govern the use of our mobile applications, ensuring a safe and transparent experience for all users.
Privacy Policy
1. Data Collection
We collect information to provide better services to all our users. This includes:
Personal Information:
Such as your name, email address, and other contact details you provide.
Usage Data:
Information on how you use our apps, including interaction data and log information.
Device Information:
Details about the devices you use to access our apps, such as hardware model, operating system, and unique device identifiers.
2. Data Usage
The information we collect is used to:
Improve and personalize our apps and services.
Communicate with you, including sending updates and promotional materials.
Analyze usage patterns to enhance user experience.
Ensure security and prevent fraud.
3. Data Sharing
We do not share your personal information with third parties except:
With your consent.
For external processing with trusted partners who comply with our privacy standards.
For legal reasons, such as complying with legal processes or government requests.
4. Data Security
We implement robust security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, no internet-based service is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
5. Your Rights
You have the right to:
Access and update your personal information.
Request deletion of your data.
Opt-out of receiving promotional communications.
Lodge a complaint with a data protection authority.
Terms of Service
1. Acceptance of Terms
By downloading or using our apps, you agree to comply with and be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree with any part of the terms, you should not use our apps.
2. User Responsibilities
You agree to:
Use the app only for lawful purposes and in accordance with these terms.
Not use the app for any harmful or malicious activities.
Respect the intellectual property rights of others.
3. License
We grant you a limited, non-exclusive, non-transferable, revocable license to use our apps for personal, non-commercial purposes.
4. Intellectual Property
All content, trademarks, and data on our apps are owned by Easy-to-Use Mobile App Studio or our licensors. You are not permitted to use any content without our prior written consent.
5. Limitation of Liability
We are not liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of our apps. This includes damages for loss of profits, data, or other intangible losses.
6. Changes to Terms
We may update our Policy and Terms from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new terms on our website or through the app. Your continued use of the app after changes are posted constitutes your acceptance of the new terms.
7. Termination
We reserve the right to terminate or suspend your access to our apps immediately, without prior notice, for conduct that we believe violates these terms or is harmful to other users or us.
